text: Andrés Felipe Aguilar Gimpel is an archer from Chile. He was born on 7 December 1996 in Santiago. Aguilar competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Andrés AguilarAndres AGUILAR == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean archers Category:Olympians for Chile Category:Sportspeople from Santiago
